Package org.springframework.data.jpa.repository

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    EntityGraph.EntityGraphType
    Enum for JPA 2.1 javax.persistence.EntityGraph types.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    EntityGraph
    Annotation to configure the JPA 2.1 javax.persistence.EntityGraphs that should be used on repository methods.
    Lock
    Annotation used to specify the LockModeType to be used when executing the query.
    Modifying
    Indicates a method should be regarded as modifying query.
    Query
    Annotation to declare finder queries directly on repository methods.
    QueryHints
    Wrapper annotation to allow QueryHint annotations to be bound to methods.
    Temporal
    Annotation to declare an appropriate TemporalType on query method parameters.
